[SPEAKER_01] Puć lišit v amgleji.

248
00:20:09,640 --> 00:20:14,180
[SPEAKER_01] Skorbi liš krugom môj.

249
00:20:14,180 --> 00:20:16,240
[SPEAKER_01] Vne vidom.

250
00:20:18,160 --> 00:20:24,059
[SPEAKER_02] Ej, budu ja stradat, mjeg, vnibedom.

251
00:20:24,059 --> 00:20:31,319
[SPEAKER_02] Vsjež ne mogu rovdati, mjeg, vnibedom.

252
00:20:31,319 --> 00:20:40,160
[SPEAKER_02] Vez sam Hristos stradal, vnibedom obješal.

253
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:45,920
[SPEAKER_02] Krasit on vincom, mjeg, vnibedom.

254
00:20:46,980 --> 00:20:54,700
[SPEAKER_02] Vez sam Hristos stradal, vnibedom obješal.

255
